## Fastest solution — embeddable Python (no install, no admin needed)

There is an **embeddable zip** version of Python — no installer, no admin, just unzip and use. Get it from any internet machine and copy it over.

**On any internet-connected machine, download this single file:**
```
https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.11.9/python-3.11.9-amd64.zip
```
Size: ~10 MB. Copy to `D:\Mr Om\Python_script\` via USB or internal share.

---

## Then on your Windows machine — 4 commands, done

**Step 1 — Unzip it:**
```cmd
cd "D:\Mr Om\Python_script"
mkdir python311
tar -xf python-3.11.9-amd64.zip -C python311
```

> `tar` is built into Windows 10/11 — no tools needed.

**Step 2 — Verify it works:**
```cmd
python311\python.exe --version
```
Expected: `Python 3.11.9`

**Step 3 — Run your script directly with full path:**
```cmd
python311\python.exe apply_repo_governance.py --dry-run
```

That's it. No installation. No admin. No PATH changes needed.

